snippet.title: Command & Conquer™ The Ultimate Collection - Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now for early access to the next Command & Conquer http://www.commandandconquer.com/collection
Get 17 games (and more!) from the best-selling real time strategy franchise of all time. Rediscover the groundbreaking, action-packed strategy gameplay that changed PC gaming forever in one great value with The Ultimate Collection. From the classic Tiberium Saga to the alternate universe of Red Alert to the modern warfare of Generals, this must-have compilation delivers a Command & Conquer experience like no other.
"One of PC Gaming's Most Beloved Franchises" -- IGN
